org.gvsig.fmap.algorithm.triangulation
Interface Triangulator

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractTriangulator, ChewTriangulator, FJenettTriangulator, OrbisGisTriangulator, PirolTriangulator, WatsonTriangulator
public interface Triangulator

Author:
Francisco José Peñarrubia (fjp@scolab.es) Interface to allow the use of several algorithms to triangulate. It will be mainly Delaunay Triangulations, but maybe in the future we can use Constrained Delaunay Triangulations (CDT), or maybe better algorithms.
